alerts.description: ...WIND ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 5 PM PST THIS AFTERNOON... * WINDS...South 20 to 30 mph with gusts up to 45 mph. * TIMING...Winds will increase this morning and peak in intensity during the afternoon. Winds will gradually subside this evening. * IMPACTS...Strong winds may blow down limbs, trees, and power lines. Scattered power outages are expected.
